snippet.title: Copycat - Gameplay Teaser / 2023
snippet.description: Copycat is wholesome, narrative-driven game about rejection, belonging and the true meaning of home. It follows the story of a newly adopted shelter cat who becomes the victim of an elaborate plan when a jealous, stray copycat steals her place in the household.
